The '''Intamm Clan''' was a [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] clan on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Rodia/Legends|Rodia]]. It was based on the [[Betu/Legends|Betu]] continent where it owned the small [[Intamm Enclave]]. It owed its loyalties to the [[Chekkoo clan/Legends|Chekkoo clan]].

